			<mod-append:choice hidden="true" max_group="1" req="FR_SHIP_LEGON_AUTO" blue="false">
				<text>Contact Federation command.</text>
				<event>
					<text>On the vidscreen appears several Federation and Engi officers, as well as Admiral Tully in the center. He recoils in shock at the sight of your ship. "An automated vessel, painted in the colors of the Legion? Vance must be going crazy... but we've received no substantial reports of this ship attacking civilians or Federation personnel. I hope this means that you're not on the Rebellion's side, and that you're willing to take on their Flagship."</text>
