			<mod-append:choice hidden="true" max_group="1" req="FR_SHIP_ZOLTAN_AUTO" blue="false">
				<text>Contact Federation command.</text>
				<event>
					<text>On the vidscreen appears several Federation and Engi officers, as well as Admiral Tully in the center. He speaks somewhat sarcastically at the sight of your ship. "The Zoltan Ministry really sent everything they could to help us, didn't they? Not even a properly staffed cruiser... Whatever, I hope you're able to take on and defeat the Flagship, because you're the only asset we have."</text>
