			<mod-append:choice hidden="true" max_group="1" req="FR_SHIP_FEDERATION_AUTO" blue="false">
				<text>Contact Federation command.</text>
				<event>
					<text>On the vidscreen appears several Federation and Engi officers, as well as Admiral Tully in the center. He looks surprised at the sight of your ship. "Our Automated Cruiser project actually succeeded? Well I never... I'm impressed that you've managed to get this far. Now, go and complete your mission. Don't let us down."</text>
					<choice hidden="true">
