			<mod-append:choice hidden="true" max_group="1" req="FR_SHIP_WATCHER" blue="false">
				<text>Contact Federation command.</text>
				<event>
					<text>On the vidscreen appears several Federation and Engi officers, as well as Admiral Tully in the center. "I... where... what's... happening? Why do I feel so... sleepy, all of a sudden? ...Oh... I heard some of the reports surrounding your ship... I won't mess with you if you don't mess with us, deal? Now, please... destroy that Flagship."</text>
