				<text>Contact Federation command.</text>
				<event>
					<text>On the vidscreen appears several Federation and Engi officers, as well as Admiral Tully in the center. "What... is that? An automated ship, obviously, yet... it feels like it's much more advanced than anything we ever made. I really hope you wish to help us, as I'm not sure if we could take you on at our current state."</text>
