				<text>Contact Federation command.</text>
				<event>
					<text>On the vidscreen appears several Federation and Engi officers, as well as Admiral Tully in the center. He looks surprised at the sight of your ship. "Wow... A ship that size made out of such rare materials is not something I would ever expect to see. Let's hope your ship fights as well as it shines."</text>
