			<mod-append:choice hidden="true" max_group="1" req="FR_SHIP_SALLY" blue="false">
				<text>Contact Federation command.</text>
				<event>
					<text>On the vidscreen appears several Federation and Engi officers, as well as Admiral Tully in the center. He jumps back at the sight of your ship. "YOU GOTTA BE KIDDING ME?! GHOST SPIDERS?! If there's anyone sentient there, then... just go destroy the Flagship... o-or, leave and never come back!"</text>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Continue...</text>
