			<mod-append:choice hidden="true" max_group="1" req="FR_SHIP_LEAH_CREWSER" blue="false">
				<text>Contact Federation command.</text>
				<event>
					<text>On the vidscreen appears several Federation and Engi officers, as well as Admiral Tully in the center. "That's a interesting paint-job for your cruiser model, don't think I've seen any out there. Oh... wait a moment, I... think I know who drives a ship like that, isn't she the daughter of some super rich Rebel guy? I wonder why she decided to aid the Federation, what with all the money her daddy has. Or... maybe you just stole it. Doesn't matter to me, all that matters is if it can take down the Flagship."</text>
