					<text>On the vidscreen appears several Federation and Engi officers, as well as Admiral Tully in the center. You can see him squinting his eyed at the screen, as if he was trying to make out the shape of your ship. "What am I supposed to be looking at? The sensor clearly says someone is there, but I can't for the life of me make out anything in the cameras. Well, whoever or whatever you are, please go take out the Flagship."</text>
