					<text>On the vidscreen appears several Federation and Engi officers, as well as Admiral Tully in the center. Everyone in the room just stares at you for a few minutes before the call ends, and the ships protecting the entrance power down their weapons letting you pass. Tully regains his consciousness just as the call ends, though he believes he willingly allowed you to pass.</text>
